text: thumb|right|240px|Christina Church The Christina Church () is a church in eastern parts of the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs to Jönköping Christina-Ljungarum Parish of the Church of Sweden and was opened on 20 April 1673. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping Category:17th-century buildings and structures
